{"type":"message","id":"6606e3df","parentId":"593343eb","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:29:44.589Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see some news headlines from Sina. Let me extract key headlines from this page. The page is quite cluttered with ads, but I can see some news headlines. Let me summarize what I can see:\n\nFrom the news section:\n- 伊朗最高领袖：血债将很快得到清算 (Iran's Supreme Leader: Blood debts will soon be settled)\n- 天坛祈年殿现\"悬日\"景观 (祈年殿 at Temple of Heaven shows \"sunrise\" phenomenon)\n- 茶农采摘春茶 (Tea farmers pick spring tea)\n- 俄军向乌阵地开火 (Russian forces fire at Ukrainian positions)\n- 伊朗袭击以公寓 (Iran attacks Israeli apartments)\n\nFrom the lists:\n- 金价大跌市民排队买金 (Gold price drops sharply, citizens line up to buy gold)\n- 伊朗何时会打出手里的\"王牌\"？ (When will Iran play its \"trump card\"?)\n- 断油危机，冲击亚洲？ (Oil cut crisis, hitting Asia?)\n- 美国打算加钱、加人，或地面入侵伊朗？ (US plans to add money, people, or ground invasion of Iran?)\n- 美军基地，\"被炸了个遍\" (US military bases, \"bombed all over\")\n- 打伊朗还要花多少？五角大楼：先再烧2000亿美元 (How much more to hit Iran? Pentagon: First burn another $200 billion)\n\n财经/科技:\n- 沪指半日跌近1% 有色金属板块集体下挫 (Shanghai index down nearly 1%, non-ferrous metals sector down)\n\n\n- AI算力需求持续火爆 阿里云上调价格 (AI computing demand continues to surge, Alibaba Cloud raises prices)\n- 腾讯2025年营收增长14% 今年AI新产品投入至少翻倍 (Tencent 2025 revenue up 14%, AI new product investment at least doubled)\n- 苹果高管今年首次访华，打卡富士康、欣旺达 (Apple executives visit China for first time this year, visit Foxconn, Sunwoda)\n- 小鹏P7新增两款车型 20.38万元起售 (XPeng P7 adds two new models, starting at 203,800 yuan)\n\nThe news coverage spans geopolitical tensions in the Middle East, tech sector momentum with AI infrastructure scaling rapidly, and notable activity in China's electric vehicle market. I should compile this into a concise morning briefing for distribution.","thinkingSignature":"10378bde64bb5b40a2fef1601484e2508b348f5011dd5dd996676e14955e4831"},{"type":"text","text":"Based on the news I can access, here's this morning's news briefing:\n\n---\n\n**📰 早间新闻简报 — 2026年3月19日**\n\n**🌍 国际**\n- **中东局势升级**：伊朗最高领袖誓言\"清算血债\"，战火燃向海湾油气腹地。五角大楼称打击伊朗需再投入2000亿美元。美军基地\"被炸了个遍\"。德国总理表示若事先知情美以开战，会提出反对。\n- **欧冠8强出炉**：皇马vs拜仁、巴黎vs利物浦、巴萨vs马竞。拜仁总分10-2亚特兰大晋级。\n\n**💼 财经**\n- **A股**：沪指半日跌近1%，有色金属板块集体下挫\n- **金价**：大幅下跌，市民排队买金\n- **阿里云**：AI算力需求火爆，上调价格\n\n**💻 科技**\n- **腾讯**：2025年营收增长14%，今年AI新产品投入至少翻倍\n- **苹果**：高管今年首次访华，访问富士康、欣旺达\n- **小鹏汽车**：P7新增两款车型，20.38万元起售\n- **汽车价格战**：宝马直降30万\n\n---\n\nThis is the news briefing for today. Due to network restrictions, I was only able to access Chinese news sources (Sina). Would you like me to send this to you, or adjust the format?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":34996,"output":797,"cacheRead":36895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72688,"cost":{"input":0.010498799999999999,"output":0.0009563999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00110685,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012562049999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773894568723}}
